text: Fungochitina is an extinct genus of chitinozoans. It was described by Taugourdeau in 1966.Fungochitina at ChitDB: Chitinozoans of Baltica. ==Species== * Fungochitina fungiformis (Eisenack, 1931) * Fungochitina kosovensis Paris et Křiž, 1984 * Fungochitina pistilliformis (Eisenack, 1931) * Fungochitina spinifera (Eisenack, 1962) ==References== Category:Prehistoric marine animals Category:Fossil taxa described in 1966
title: Fungochitina
